        public void FILTER_USER_STORAGE_SUMMARY_BY_USERNAME_TC()
        Summary
        Filter user storage summary by userName
        Pre-Conditions
        DashBoard page should be open
        User should have administrator rights
        Steps
        1. Click on UserName on right upper corner of browser window
        2. Click on 'Reports'
        3. Navigate to 'User Storage Summary'
        4. Enter user name
        5. Click on Search button
        Expected Result:
        1. Verify that data should be retrieved as per user name entered
